name: Rescue Ferret
desc: You can shuffle this card you control into the Deck; Special Summon any number of monsters from your Deck whose total Levels equal exactly 6, except "Rescue Ferret", to your zone(s) a Link Monster(s) points to, but they have their effects negated, also they are destroyed during the End Phase. You can only use this effect of "Rescue Ferret" once per turn.
